OL,6,FWhat happened in the 1944 crash?
OL,8,FThe 19-year-old Norwegian pilot
OL,9,FSeargeant Kai Arthur Knagenhjelm had
OL,10,Fbeen carrying out practice attacks
OL,11,Fwith a fellow Spitfire at 5,000 feet
OL,12,Ffor around half an hour.
OL,14,FWhen he returned to RAF Eshott,
OL,15,FSergeant Knagenhjelm was in a circuit,
OL,16,Fawaiting instructions to land.
